	<div class="col-sm-10 col-md-10 col-lg-10 post-content" component="post/content">
		<h3><a class="anchor-offset" name="code-l2cap_connection_request-code"></a><code>L2CAP_Connection_Request</code></h3>
<pre><code class="language-text">00000181	0.82300282	** RT_CompletionRoutineUrbSubmit: Irp: 0x854DC8B8 - IOCTL_INTERNAL_USB_SUBMIT_URB - URB_FUNCTION_BULK_OR_INTERRUPT_TRANSFER - Status STATUS_SUCCESS - Buffer: 0x85703000, MDL: 0x887905F0, Length: 0x10, Pipe:0x85A2137C, Flags: 0x3.	
00000182	0.82301444	** 42 20 0C 00 08 00 01 00  02 01 04 00 11 00 40 7C  B ............@|	
00000183	0.82302463	** 42 20 0C 00 08 00 01 00  02 01 04 00 11 00 40 7C  B ............@|	
00000184	0.82304817	** Irp: 0x854DC8B8 - IOCTL_INTERNAL_USB_SUBMIT_URB - URB_FUNCTION_BULK_OR_INTERRUPT_TRANSFER. Buffer: 0x878B3000, MDL: 0x0, Length: 0x1000, Pipe:0x85A2137C, Flags: 0x3.	
</code></pre>
<p dir="auto">This gets repeated over and over again, so either the correct answer is missing in the trace or not sent at all.</p>

	</div>
	
