	<div class="col-sm-10 col-md-10 col-lg-10 post-content" component="post/content">
		<p dir="auto">This <code>.INF</code> section will add driver as a lower class filter driver for the <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-hardware/drivers/install/system-defined-device-setup-classes-available-to-vendors" rel="nofollow ugc">Bluetooth</a> class (GUID: <code>{e0cbf06c-cd8b-4647-bb8a-263b43f0f974}</code>) and load it on every <code>BTHUSB</code> host device:</p>
<pre><code class="language-ini">[Filter_Device.NT.HW]
AddReg = Filter_AddReg

[Filter_AddReg]
HKLM,SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Class\{e0cbf06c-cd8b-4647-bb8a-263b43f0f974},LowerFilters,0x00010008,Filter
</code></pre>
<p dir="auto">Section for uninstallation missing.</p>
<p dir="auto"><strong>EDIT:</strong> obsolete, will do this via helper tool instead of INF file.</p>

	</div>
	
