	<div class="col-sm-10 col-md-10 col-lg-10 post-content" component="post/content">
		<p dir="auto">I abandoned the Bluetooth Profile Driver idea to soon; let's see what this skeleton can do for me <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f914.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--thinking_face" title=":thinking_face:" alt="🤔" /></p>
<p dir="auto"><a class="lightboxlink" href="/assets/uploads/files/1546352010306-9a0cde3c-1002-4d22-baf5-c52f9f1aba30-image.png" data-lightbox="0_1546352012177_9a0cde3c-1002-4d22-baf5-c52f9f1aba30-image.png"><img class="lightboximage" src="/assets/uploads/files/1546352010306-9a0cde3c-1002-4d22-baf5-c52f9f1aba30-image.png" alt="0_1546352012177_9a0cde3c-1002-4d22-baf5-c52f9f1aba30-image.png" /></a></p>

