		<div class="author">
			<a href="/user/nefarius">
			nefarius
		</a>
		
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="col-sm-10 col-md-10 col-lg-10 post-content" component="post/content">
		<blockquote>
<p dir="auto">PSMs shall be odd and the least significant bit of the most significant byte shall be zero, hence the following ranges do not contain valid PSMs: 0x0100-0x01FF, 0x0300-0x03FF, 0x0500-0x05FF, 0x0700-0x07FF, 0x0900-0x09FF, 0x0B00-0x0BFF, 0x0D00-0x0DFF, 0x0F00-0x0FFF. All even values are also not valid as PSMs.</p>
</blockquote>

	</div>
	
