<p dir="auto">Which generates some more noise in the profile driver:</p>
<pre><code class="language-text">2019/01/05-21:13:01.379	TRACE_LEVEL_VERBOSE	BthPS3IndicationCallback Entry
2019/01/05-21:13:01.379	TRACE_LEVEL_INFORMATION	BthPS3IndicationCallback ++ IndicationRemoteConnect
