<p dir="auto">Now ofc. the state machine I ripped off the <code>bthecho</code> sample driver goes crazy here and the connection drops but both channels connection requests actually bubble up to our driver, that's good news <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f642.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--slightly_smiling_face" title=":slightly_smiling_face:" alt="🙂" /></p>

	</div>
	
