<p dir="auto">Right, so the connection handshake works for both Control and Interrupt channel, now I need to copypasta <em>a ton</em> of code  to send and respond to the configuration requests. And extend the state machine to handle two channels instead of one like the example code intended. Oh dear <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f440.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--eyes" title=":eyes:" alt="👀" /></p>

