	<div class="col-sm-10 col-md-10 col-lg-10 post-content" component="post/content">
		<h2><a class="anchor-offset" name="working-on-bthps3util"></a>Working on BthPS3Util</h2>
<p dir="auto">Creating a small command line utility for abstracting away the mess of creating filter device node, installing filter driver, enabling the filter and registering the service profile.</p>
<p dir="auto"><a class="lightboxlink" href="/assets/uploads/files/1547897265889-3235ea5f-c436-4f3f-8969-a3b90a480c5c-image.png" data-lightbox="0_1547897266264_3235ea5f-c436-4f3f-8969-a3b90a480c5c-image.png"><img class="lightboximage" src="/assets/uploads/files/1547897265889-3235ea5f-c436-4f3f-8969-a3b90a480c5c-image.png" alt="0_1547897266264_3235ea5f-c436-4f3f-8969-a3b90a480c5c-image.png" /></a></p>
<p dir="auto"><a class="lightboxlink" href="/assets/uploads/files/1547308196495-3fe40c51-c0ad-4bfa-98ae-0863ad41b749-image.png" data-lightbox="0_1547308197893_3fe40c51-c0ad-4bfa-98ae-0863ad41b749-image.png"><img class="lightboximage" src="/assets/uploads/files/1547308196495-3fe40c51-c0ad-4bfa-98ae-0863ad41b749-image.png" alt="0_1547308197893_3fe40c51-c0ad-4bfa-98ae-0863ad41b749-image.png" /></a></p>
