		<p dir="auto">Oddly enough I wasn't able to find an official way to get the remote device name from an incoming connection, just the MAC address. This isn't a showstopper but odd and annoying for device identification. Or am I missing something <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f914.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--thinking_face" title=":thinking_face:" alt="🤔" /></p>

