		<p dir="auto">I'm feeling a cold creeping up on me but nevertheless managed to utilize enough brain power to implement resource cleanup on disconnect without a single BSOD! <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f920.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--face_with_cowboy_hat" title=":face_with_cowboy_hat:" alt="🤠" /></p>
