<p dir="auto">'till next time <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f44b.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--wave" title=":wave:" alt="👋" /></p>

