		<h2><a class="anchor-offset" name="biggest-struggle-in-this-project-so-far-img-src-https-forums-vigem-org-assets-plugins-nodebb-plugin-emoji-emoji-apple-1f606-png-v-hmq6eelgc4s-class-not-responsive-emoji-emoji-apple-emoji-laughing-title-laughing-alt"></a>Biggest struggle in this project so far <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f606.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--laughing" title=":laughing:" alt="😆" /></h2>
<p dir="auto"><a class="lightboxlink" href="/assets/uploads/files/1549011126625-1bd58b96-8320-4453-b860-2170d0b5b56c-image.png" data-lightbox="1bd58b96-8320-4453-b860-2170d0b5b56c-image.png"><img class="lightboximage" src="/assets/uploads/files/1549011126625-1bd58b96-8320-4453-b860-2170d0b5b56c-image.png" alt="1bd58b96-8320-4453-b860-2170d0b5b56c-image.png" /></a></p>

