	<div class="col-sm-10 col-md-10 col-lg-10 post-content" component="post/content">
		<p dir="auto">A <strong>lot</strong> of progress was made today. Nothing much to present yet but I've basically started to design and implement the interface that will be used to talk to the exposed PDOs via own function driver. This causes the code base for the profile driver remain encapsulated for Bluetooth related stuff only. Higher level functions (HID mini-driver, LED, Rumble, ...) will then be implemented by one or more individual function drivers latching onto the PDOs.</p>
<p dir="auto">Cheers</p>

