<p dir="auto"><a class="lightboxlink" href="/assets/uploads/files/1550774873497-fb2e64d0-a643-4c1f-bbeb-1258dc7c6827-image.png" data-lightbox="fb2e64d0-a643-4c1f-bbeb-1258dc7c6827-image.png"><img class="lightboximage" src="/assets/uploads/files/1550774873497-fb2e64d0-a643-4c1f-bbeb-1258dc7c6827-image.png" alt="fb2e64d0-a643-4c1f-bbeb-1258dc7c6827-image.png" /></a></p>
<p dir="auto">Pool tag details:</p>
<pre><code class="language-text">BTHP - bthport.sys  - Bluetooth port driver (generic)
HCIT - bthport.sys  - Bluetooth port driver (HCI)
</code></pre>
<p dir="auto">Now if the symbols could download faster than over 56k I could actually see more <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f4a4.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--zzz" title=":zzz:" alt="💤" /></p>

