	<div class="col-sm-10 col-md-10 col-lg-10 post-content" component="post/content">
		<p dir="auto">How future proof is this filter solution? Do you think it is possible for Windows to make such a change in a update that could break it or you think that is unlikely or just straight up impossible unless windows change in a fundamental way?</p>
<p dir="auto">Sorry if this is no place to ask or if my question does not make much sense. I am no developer/coder in any meaningful way, but I know just enough about coding to understand your posts here and I find it really interesting to know how this actually works. I would really appreciate to hear your thoughts on this with some insight on why and how windows could or couldn't break this in the near future.<br />
Also, thanks for your work on the ScpToolKit and on maintaining this posts on the development! I find myself refreshing this page many times a day just to see your explanations on how you are making your way through this.</p>

