		<p dir="auto">Alright, breakfast is done, back to work <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f60b.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--yum" title=":yum:" alt="😋" /> Looks like disabling the patching is working as expected:</p>
<pre><code class="language-text">2019/05/18-11:29:22.504	TRACE_LEVEL_VERBOSE	UrbFunctionBulkInTransferCompleted Entry
2019/05/18-11:29:22.504	TRACE_LEVEL_VERBOSE	&gt;&gt; Connection request for HID Control PSM 0x0011 arrived
2019/05/18-11:29:22.504	TRACE_LEVEL_VERBOSE	-- NOT Patching HID Control PSM
