		<p dir="auto">Aha! Deception! It actually <em>was</em> VMware! <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f632.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--astonished" title=":astonished:" alt="😲" /> On a physical Windows 10 machine it works flawlessly like expected even with a 5 meter USB repeater:</p>
