2019/05/19-17:54:25.649	TRACE_LEVEL_VERBOSE	L2CAP_PS3_ConnectionIndicationCallback Exit
--------------------------- Device connection dropped, all memory freed ---------------------------
</code></pre>
<p dir="auto">Nice, the list is getting shorter <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f604.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--smile" title=":smile:" alt="😄" /></p>

