		<p dir="auto">Dammit, almost... <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f440.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--eyes" title=":eyes:" alt="👀" /></p>
<p dir="auto"><a class="lightboxlink" href="/assets/uploads/files/1560706824738-vmware_zktak1rimb.png" data-lightbox="vmware_ZKTaK1RimB.png"><img class="lightboximage" src="/assets/uploads/files/1560706824738-vmware_zktak1rimb.png" alt="vmware_ZKTaK1RimB.png" /></a></p>
<p dir="auto">What's going on here....</p>
<pre><code class="language-text">STACK_TEXT:  
nt!DbgBreakPoint
