<p dir="auto">Oh <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f610.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--neutral_face" title=":neutral_face:" alt="😐" /> How did I manage to provoke that. Well, back to fixing stuff <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f605.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--sweat_smile" title=":sweat_smile:" alt="😅" /></p>

