	<div class="col-sm-10 col-md-10 col-lg-10 post-content" component="post/content">
		<p dir="auto"><a class="plugin-mentions-user plugin-mentions-a" href="https://forums.vigem.org/uid/1">@nefarius</a> Shibari was crashing when disconnecting a controller by bluetooth or when an connected controller by bluetooth was connected then by USB, I remember it spawned 2 controllers in this situation or something like that.<br />
Unless these issues can be really easily fixed in a day or two, I'd vote for you to focus on the release with no companion app, even if it takes longer.<br />
Good luck, Nefarius, and have a nice day!</p>

