	<div class="col-sm-10 col-md-10 col-lg-10 post-content" component="post/content">
		<p dir="auto"><a class="plugin-mentions-user plugin-mentions-a" href="https://forums.vigem.org/uid/155">@epikvigem</a> there's a few topics who threw off the schedule:</p>
<ul>
<li>Windows 10 1903 changes apparently breaking kernel drivers left and right. Did quite a bit of research on that to break through all the misinformation on the web.</li>
<li>WHQL lab advances. This took the most time, setting up the lab and running a lot of tests. Tedious and costly.</li>
<li>Working on paid commissions. Ever since I've started the business I'm also doing contracted work. That wins ofc. over this hobby-ish fun topic as this stuff doesn't pay the bills as long as the Patreon and other sources of income are low <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f609.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--wink" title=":wink:" alt="😉" /> That's just how life is. More funds, more speed. Simple formula.</li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto">Cheers</p>

