	<div class="col-sm-10 col-md-10 col-lg-10 post-content" component="post/content">
		<h1><a class="anchor-offset" name="pairing-devices-to-bthps3"></a>Pairing devices to BthPS3</h1>
<p dir="auto">Useful link collection for later <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f603.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--smiley" title=":smiley:" alt="😃" /></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://macaddresschanger.com/how-to-find-bluetooth-mac-address-windows" rel="nofollow ugc">How to find Bluetooth MAC Address in Windows</a></li>
<li><a href="http://dancingpixelstudios.com/sixaxis-controller/sixaxispairtool/" rel="nofollow ugc">SIXAXISPAIRTOOL</a></li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto">Far more comfortable than SCP or going through FireShock <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f607.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--innocent" title=":innocent:" alt="😇" /></p>

	</div>
	
</div>
<div class="row post-footer">
	<div class="col-xs-12">
		<div class="pull-left">
			
		</div>
		<div class="pull-right">
