	<div class="col-sm-10 col-md-10 col-lg-10 post-content" component="post/content">
		<p dir="auto">Ha! Gotcha!</p>
<p dir="auto"><a class="lightboxlink" href="/assets/uploads/files/1572448798287-9ea09b9b-922c-4543-b3aa-360fe78bd31f-image.png" data-lightbox="9ea09b9b-922c-4543-b3aa-360fe78bd31f-image.png"><img class="lightboximage" src="/assets/uploads/files/1572448798287-9ea09b9b-922c-4543-b3aa-360fe78bd31f-image.png" alt="9ea09b9b-922c-4543-b3aa-360fe78bd31f-image.png" /></a></p>
<p dir="auto"><a class="lightboxlink" href="/assets/uploads/files/1572448876822-4be904d9-1fa3-40f0-9f8c-822274612aad-image.png" data-lightbox="4be904d9-1fa3-40f0-9f8c-822274612aad-image.png"><img class="lightboximage" src="/assets/uploads/files/1572448876822-4be904d9-1fa3-40f0-9f8c-822274612aad-image.png" alt="4be904d9-1fa3-40f0-9f8c-822274612aad-image.png" /></a></p>
<p dir="auto">Building those submission CAB files feels like ancient magic once you haven't done it for a couple of months but I got it <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f607.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--innocent" title=":innocent:" alt="😇" /></p>

