	<div class="col-sm-10 col-md-10 col-lg-10 post-content" component="post/content">
		<p dir="auto">Some cosmetic improvements <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f603.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--smiley" title=":smiley:" alt="😃" /> Created a NULL driver INF for the child devices:</p>
<p dir="auto"><a class="lightboxlink" href="/assets/uploads/files/1574547171703-3172fbb2-6842-4e74-a0d4-7cbefcaee198-image.png" data-lightbox="3172fbb2-6842-4e74-a0d4-7cbefcaee198-image.png"><img class="lightboximage" src="/assets/uploads/files/1574547171703-3172fbb2-6842-4e74-a0d4-7cbefcaee198-image.png" alt="3172fbb2-6842-4e74-a0d4-7cbefcaee198-image.png" /></a></p>
<p dir="auto"><a class="lightboxlink" href="/assets/uploads/files/1574547184073-0a53b3c4-5e75-4183-98f1-164ce60252bb-image.png" data-lightbox="0a53b3c4-5e75-4183-98f1-164ce60252bb-image.png"><img class="lightboximage" src="/assets/uploads/files/1574547184073-0a53b3c4-5e75-4183-98f1-164ce60252bb-image.png" alt="0a53b3c4-5e75-4183-98f1-164ce60252bb-image.png" /></a></p>
<p dir="auto"><a class="lightboxlink" href="/assets/uploads/files/1574547228769-d7be0894-7e77-4524-a47f-3e91af494a4c-image.png" data-lightbox="d7be0894-7e77-4524-a47f-3e91af494a4c-image.png"><img class="lightboximage" src="/assets/uploads/files/1574547228769-d7be0894-7e77-4524-a47f-3e91af494a4c-image.png" alt="d7be0894-7e77-4524-a47f-3e91af494a4c-image.png" /></a></p>
<p dir="auto"><a class="lightboxlink" href="/assets/uploads/files/1574547237973-eb4d519b-6085-4e12-b0e6-c215e0512e64-image.png" data-lightbox="eb4d519b-6085-4e12-b0e6-c215e0512e64-image.png"><img class="lightboximage" src="/assets/uploads/files/1574547237973-eb4d519b-6085-4e12-b0e6-c215e0512e64-image.png" alt="eb4d519b-6085-4e12-b0e6-c215e0512e64-image.png" /></a></p>
<p dir="auto">Quite slick if I may say so <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f60f.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--smirk" title=":smirk:" alt="😏" /></p>
<p dir="auto">I'm still polishing the release and haven't died yet, so no worries! <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f61c.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--stuck_out_tongue_winking_eye" title=":stuck_out_tongue_winking_eye:" alt="😜" /></p>
<p dir="auto">Cheers</p>

	</div>
	
