	<div class="col-sm-10 col-md-10 col-lg-10 post-content" component="post/content">
		<p dir="auto">I've received a valid concern that the use of trademarked names like "PlayStation(R) 3" could raise unnecessary conflict so I decided to push yet another update removing those and put emphasis in the "not by Sony"-nature of the project <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f609.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--wink" title=":wink:" alt="😉" /> Not my intention to step on anybody's feet and am not skilled enough in trademark laws and exceptions to take the risk.</p>
<p dir="auto">Cheers</p>

