<p dir="auto"><a href="https://forums.vigem.org/projects/bthps3">I did a thingy, enjoy!</a> <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f601.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--grin" title=":grin:" alt="😁" /> Thanks to anybody following my journey and already donating, hugs and kisses <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f618.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--kissing_heart" title=":kissing_heart:" alt="😘" /></p>
<p dir="auto">I'll now vanish into winter vacation, cheers!</p>

