	<div class="col-sm-10 col-md-10 col-lg-10 post-content" component="post/content">
		<p dir="auto"><a class="plugin-mentions-user plugin-mentions-a" href="https://forums.vigem.org/uid/219">@Luke76bg</a> it is <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/263a.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--relaxed" title=":relaxed:" alt="☺" />️ but like mentioned many many times before, DS4 isn't the primary focus of this solution and TouchPad functionality is out of the scope of this <img src="https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f618.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s" class="not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--kissing_heart" title=":kissing_heart:" alt="😘" /></p>

