unction must access paged memory)<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Ouch! How evil! <img src=\"https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f605.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s\" class=\"not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--sweat_smile\" title=\":sweat_smile:\" alt=\"😅\" /> So that can totally happen and <code>!wdfkd.wdflogdump<\/code> gives clear insights:<\/p>\n<pre><code>1: kd&gt; !wdfkd.wdflogdump BthPS3\n...\n37: FxVerifierCheckIrqlLevel - Called at wrong IRQL; at level 2, should be at level 0\n---- end of log ----\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Right, so this would've fallen under the radar if it didn't bomb in the lab. Thanks, WHQL <img src=\"https://forums.vigem.org/assets/plugins/nodebb-plugin-emoji/emoji/apple/1f61d.png?v=hmq6eelgc4s\" class=\"not-responsive emoji emoji-apple emoji--stuck_out_tongue_closed_eyes\" title=\":stuck_out_tongue_closed_eyes:\" alt=\"😝\" /> Onward with the fixes!<\/p>\n","upvotes":0,"timestamp":1552213407534,"deleted":0,"replies":{"hasMore":false,"users":[],"text":"[[topic:one_reply_to_this_post]]","count":0},"bookmarks":0,"index":61,"eventStart":1552213407534,"eventEnd":1552237830960,"user":{"uid":1,"username":"nefarius","userslug":"nefarius","reputation":178,"postcount":875,"topiccount":105,"picture":"/assets/uploads/profile/1-profileavatar.png","signature":"","banned":false,"banned:expire":0,"status":"offline","lastonline":1659566870722,"groupTitle":"[\"\"]","displayname":"nefarius","groupTitleArray":[""],"icon:text":"N","icon:bgColor":"#1b5e20","lastonlineISO":"2022-08-03T22:47:50.722Z","banned_until":0,"banned_until_readable":"Not Banned","selectedGroups":[],"custom_profile_info":[]},"bookmarked":false,"upvoted":false,"downvoted":false,"selfPost":false,"topicOwnerPost":true,"display_edit_tools":false,"display_delete_tools":false,"display_moderator_tools":false,"display_move_tools":false,"display_post_menu":0},{"timestamp":1552237830960,"replies":{"hasMore":false,"users":[{"uid":1,"username":"nefarius",